snippet.title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - VGX Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch this brand new video showing The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt in action! 
The VGX Trailer offers an extended peak into the adventure to come in the third installment of The Witcher saga.

You can download the HD version at http://bit.ly/1ckcQw0

The game is scheduled to launch May 19, 2015 and will be available on Xbox One, PC and PlayStation®4.

See also:
Debut Gameplay Trailer at http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZ_G6XiHoUA
Killing Monsters Cinematic Trailer at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c0i88t0Kacs
The Beginning at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2HGhm0H7d68
